headline: Research Tools & Consumables Stocks Q2 Teardown: Agilent (NYSE:A) Vs The Rest
summary: As the craze of earnings season draws to a close, here’s a look back at some of the most exciting (and some less so) results from Q2. Today, we are looking at research tools & consumables stocks, starting with Agilent (NYSE:A).
